/GfD36_nUqM3wBSphR_tNKz7jA5w=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/Joseph-Duggar-Sheriff-Tommy-Ford-032026-7b89c8f2ee5c47d5b1cbac3ac8ee0b9d.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 17:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/joseph-duggar-sheriff-dont-care-tv-show-11930841</guid></item><item><title>艾米·杜格·金 (Amy Duggar King) 对约瑟夫表弟因猥亵儿童指控被捕感到“恶心”，但“并不感到惊讶”</title><link>https://people.com/amy-duggar-king-speaks-out-joseph-duggar-arrest-11930631</link><description>《19个孩子和计数》的演员约瑟夫·杜加尔于3月18日星期三被捕&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://people.com/thmb/bp1VUM6lbHguCRC2bx4a2M8ZUB8=/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():format(jpeg)/amy-duggar-joseph-duggar-032026-1-0026a41be612401192efe2f3ce965328.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 19:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://people.com/amy-duggar-king-speaks-out-joseph-duggar-arrest-11930631</guid></item></channel></rss>